{"tid":522852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家BOOKMARK呢條魚蛋革命嘅小販訪問","createTime":"2018-01-08T02:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:20:23.000Z","uid":53687,"like":99,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0d968501af3e2d6bb65da9829441d55a47dd8800","tid":522852,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDe5NBT1JCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUDe5NBT1JCU&d=Obgldri6mh5%2FSbhtWCMOBjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7b416068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDe5NBT1JCU</a><br />\n<br />\n成日見到有人一討論魚革時，就話小販一面倒咁屌本土派搞事，<br />\n但呢段片嘅三個小販，全部都無屌本土派累及佢哋，仲講得出政府先係源頭，<br />\n嗱，我唔會話一定無小販屌本土派，但絕對唔係好似某啲人所講，係一面倒屌本土派，<br />\n大家BOOKMARK呢條片，一有人講類似嘅嘢，即刻POST返出嚟。"},{"pid":"a5cc76e36e9157397bf6aa5f0e6dd2310ccc4ecf","tid":522852,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfea62a37bb7286b0cf579efa3f2eff56e37507","tid":522852,"uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"點解毒果 + CCTVB 永遠只會出到 屌獨派既小販訪問, <br />\n<br />\n而BBC可以出到正常小販訪問？<br />\n<br />\n咁神奇？ 個編輯定記者既問題？"},{"pid":"23bc3e1f80a7a5e21eaad2c944e05f576ec1ead8","tid":522852,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91f16a0e12dd4bcd7317a297fb65d053975b564","tid":522852,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0dfea62a37bb7286b0cf579efa3f2eff56e37507","tid":522852,"uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"點解毒果 + CCTVB 永遠只會出到 屌獨派既小販訪問, <br />\n<br />\n而BBC可以出到正常小販訪問？<br />\n<br />\n咁神奇？ 個編輯定記者既問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:36:42.000Z","msg":